    <!--============================== Main Content =================================-->
    <div id="main-content">
        <br>
        <div id="bai-ganio">
           <h1>
               Bai Ganio is a fictional character & protagonist in
               <br>
               <a href="#" class="BulgariaModernaV3" data-toggle="tooltip" data-placement="top"
                  title="Aleko Ivanitsov Konstantinov known under the alias 'Lucky', a Bulgarian writer, lawyer and a public man.
               Born in the town of Svishtov on January 13th year of 1863.">
                   Aleko Konstantinov's
               </a>
               series of satirical feuilletons.
           </h1>
           <hr class="custom-fancy">
           <h3>
               "Do not despise this simple, sly, pricey wretch,
               he's brainchild of the harsh environment, victim of rough educators.
               <br>
               The evil is not within himself, but within the influence of the environment.
               Bai Ganio is powerful, thoughtful, perceptive - mostly receptive!
               <br>
               Put him under the influence of a good leader, and you will see what a feats he is able to do.
               <br>
               Bai Ganio is manifested so far only with his primitive animal energy,
               but he is keeping within a large pool of spiritual force,
               that expects only a moral impulse to become a living force...".
               <br>

               <hr class="custom-fancy">
              <span style="float: right"> - by the feuilleton "Bai Ganio in Russia" - A. Konstantinov</span>
           </h3>
       </div>
        <br>
        <br>
    </div>
